The Quiet Sea
A quiet sea  
Under an expansive sky,  
Mirrors the thoughts  
Of a wandering soul,  
Each wave a whisper,  
A soft sigh,  
Guiding the heart onward  
Into the unknown.

---Stephen Crane

- Stephen Crane
